title: Enable Comments on User Page
description: Enable comments on user pages that are created automatically.
...

 - **Step 1:** Create a page file with no contents named as the [user][link:../reference/extension/user] `path` value [^1].
 - **Step 2:** Create the page children files with no contents named as the user page slug you want to enable the comments.

~~~ .txt
.\
 └── lot\
     └── page\
         ├── …
         ├── user\
         │   └── ta-tau-taufik.page
         └── user.page
~~~

[^1]: You can get the user `path` value in the user extension configuration file.